{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-jsx","path":"/blog/taza-chocolate-factory-tour","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>I don't know how many of you have heard of Taza Chocolate, but up in Somerville and Cambridge, they've become a pretty big deal among the hip chocolate crowd.  I've  seen Taza Chocolates at airports and according to my tour guide, Taza is actually sold in all 50 states.  In addition, the brand is sold internationally in countries including Switzerland, and even more humbling, Mexico.</p>\n<p>I say \"even more humbling\" because the idea of Taza Chocolate was based on the stoneground Mexican chocolate that Taza's founder, Alex Whitmore, had when he was traveling in Oaxaca, Mexico.  The story is pretty unique because Alex actually ended up apprenticing under an Oaxacan stone miller to learn how to make the grinding stones which he uses for the Taza chocolates today.  All the grinding stones used at the factory are hand carved by Alex right behind the factory in Somerville...talk about local!  Still, it's a great story because you have this guy who was clearly inspired enough by something to start a business out of it.  He takes the time to really put in that effort - to learn about the business - to learn how to carve stones from molinero masters - and then come back to Somerville to create something truly special for the public.</p>\n<h4 id=\"hand-carved-milling-stone-cacao-podstaza-chocolate--each-cacao-pod-weighs-about-a-pound-to-a-pound-and-a-half\"><a href=\"#hand-carved-milling-stone-cacao-podstaza-chocolate--each-cacao-pod-weighs-about-a-pound-to-a-pound-and-a-half\" aria-label=\"hand carved milling stone cacao podstaza chocolate  each cacao pod weighs about a pound to a pound and a half permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Hand-Carved Milling Stone, Cacao Pods,Taza Chocolate.  Each cacao pod weighs about a pound to a pound and a half.</h4>\n<figure> <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 710px;\">\n      <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/4113d05eb2fa58b9d20cc5f49895b4fc/f3481/81-13.jpg\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 100%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/jpeg;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"81 13\" title=\"81 13\" src=\"/static/4113d05eb2fa58b9d20cc5f49895b4fc/f3481/81-13.jpg\" srcset=\"/static/4113d05eb2fa58b9d20cc5f49895b4fc/90185/81-13.jpg 450w,\n/static/4113d05eb2fa58b9d20cc5f49895b4fc/f3481/81-13.jpg 710w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 710px) 100vw, 710px\" loading=\"lazy\">\n  </a>\n    </span> </figure>\n<p>If you haven't tried Taza Chocolate, I would suggest you go and give it a try.  Taza doesn't add any soy or dairy to their chocolates and because it is stone ground, all the chocolates have this coarse \"stone ground\" texture to them, which is pretty neat.  And because they work with quality cacao beans from Latin and South America, the actual chocolate flavor is much more pronounced.  So yes, this is not your Nestle or Hershey's chocolate chocolate - nor would you want it to be.  It is an experience when you eat it, and that's really the effect that all chocolate should have when eaten. </p>\n<h4 id=\"a-variety-of-chocolates-at-the-taza-shop\"><a href=\"#a-variety-of-chocolates-at-the-taza-shop\" aria-label=\"a variety of chocolates at the taza shop permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>A Variety of Chocolates at the Taza Shop</h4>\n<figure> <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 533px;\">\n      <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/0565b09b1637267ae67774c84136d8dc/04993/81-15.jpg\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 75.046904315197%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/jpeg;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"81 15\" title=\"81 15\" src=\"/static/0565b09b1637267ae67774c84136d8dc/04993/81-15.jpg\" srcset=\"/static/0565b09b1637267ae67774c84136d8dc/90185/81-15.jpg 450w,\n/static/0565b09b1637267ae67774c84136d8dc/04993/81-15.jpg 533w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 533px) 100vw, 533px\" loading=\"lazy\">\n  </a>\n    </span> </figure>\n<p>If you don't know stores that carry it, I'm sure you can give Taza's customer service a call to find out.  The business is expanding, but Taza is definitely not a \"corporate chocolate factory\" factory, nor do I think they  want to be.  It is still quite small with just several rooms and the feel is still very local, which is great.</p>\n<h4 id=\"this-was-hilarious-because-prior-to-the-tour-everyone-had-to-put-on-hair-nets-and-for-those-with-beardstaza-actually-has-beard-nets-as-well\"><a href=\"#this-was-hilarious-because-prior-to-the-tour-everyone-had-to-put-on-hair-nets-and-for-those-with-beardstaza-actually-has-beard-nets-as-well\" aria-label=\"this was hilarious because prior to the tour everyone had to put on hair nets and for those with beardstaza actually has beard nets as well permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>This was hilarious because prior to the tour, everyone had to put on hair nets, and for those with beards...Taza actually has beard nets as well!</h4>\n<figure> <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 653px;\">\n      <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/72b4893fc28006957d89119189585cab/0e887/81-2.jpg\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 75.03828483920367%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/jpeg;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"81 2\" title=\"81 2\" src=\"/static/72b4893fc28006957d89119189585cab/0e887/81-2.jpg\" srcset=\"/static/72b4893fc28006957d89119189585cab/90185/81-2.jpg 450w,\n/static/72b4893fc28006957d89119189585cab/0e887/81-2.jpg 653w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 653px) 100vw, 653px\" loading=\"lazy\">\n  </a>\n    </span> </figure>\n<h4 id=\"the-wall-explaining-taza-chocolate-from-tree-to-packaged-chocolate\"><a href=\"#the-wall-explaining-taza-chocolate-from-tree-to-packaged-chocolate\" aria-label=\"the wall explaining taza chocolate from tree to packaged chocolate permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>The wall explaining Taza chocolate from tree to packaged chocolate.</h4>\n<figure> <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 653px;\">\n      <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/a317093df19b4d86f1851565445df5e0/0e887/81-14.jpg\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 75.03828483920367%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/jpeg;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"81 14\" title=\"81 14\" src=\"/static/a317093df19b4d86f1851565445df5e0/0e887/81-14.jpg\" srcset=\"/static/a317093df19b4d86f1851565445df5e0/90185/81-14.jpg 450w,\n/static/a317093df19b4d86f1851565445df5e0/0e887/81-14.jpg 653w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 653px) 100vw, 653px\" loading=\"lazy\">\n  </a>\n    </span> </figure>\n<h4 id=\"bags-of-cacao-beans-each-weighing-500-pounds\"><a href=\"#bags-of-cacao-beans-each-weighing-500-pounds\" aria-label=\"bags of cacao beans each weighing 500 pounds permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Bags of cacao beans each weighing 500 pounds.</h4>\n<figure> <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 653px;\">\n      <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/76333cc68f6b1ae3333f92876baaaa76/0e887/81-5.jpg\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 75.03828483920367%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/jpeg;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"81 5\" title=\"81 5\" src=\"/static/76333cc68f6b1ae3333f92876baaaa76/0e887/81-5.jpg\" srcset=\"/static/76333cc68f6b1ae3333f92876baaaa76/90185/81-5.jpg 450w,\n/static/76333cc68f6b1ae3333f92876baaaa76/0e887/81-5.jpg 653w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 653px) 100vw, 653px\" loading=\"lazy\">\n  </a>\n    </span> </figure>\n<h4 id=\"winnowing-machine-separating-cacao-shell-from-the-cacao-nibs\"><a href=\"#winnowing-machine-separating-cacao-shell-from-the-cacao-nibs\" aria-label=\"winnowing machine separating cacao shell from the cacao nibs permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Winnowing machine separating cacao shell from the cacao nibs.</h4>\n<figure> <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 710px;\">\n      <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/2c54395af31165d1afda6b5089b19f4d/f3481/81-10.jpg\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 75.07042253521126%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/jpeg;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"81 10\" title=\"81 10\" src=\"/static/2c54395af31165d1afda6b5089b19f4d/f3481/81-10.jpg\" srcset=\"/static/2c54395af31165d1afda6b5089b19f4d/90185/81-10.jpg 450w,\n/static/2c54395af31165d1afda6b5089b19f4d/f3481/81-10.jpg 710w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 710px) 100vw, 710px\" loading=\"lazy\">\n  </a>\n    </span> </figure>\n<h4 id=\"cacao-nibs-for-sampling--tastes-a-bit-like-crunchy-coffee-beans\"><a href=\"#cacao-nibs-for-sampling--tastes-a-bit-like-crunchy-coffee-beans\" aria-label=\"cacao nibs for sampling  tastes a bit like crunchy coffee beans permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Cacao nibs for sampling!  Tastes a bit like crunchy coffee beans.</h4>\n<figure> <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 685px;\">\n      <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/00db6facbab33ef970be1c853fa82112/45ec0/81-6.jpg\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 100%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/jpeg;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"81 6\" title=\"81 6\" src=\"/static/00db6facbab33ef970be1c853fa82112/45ec0/81-6.jpg\" srcset=\"/static/00db6facbab33ef970be1c853fa82112/90185/81-6.jpg 450w,\n/static/00db6facbab33ef970be1c853fa82112/45ec0/81-6.jpg 685w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 685px) 100vw, 685px\" loading=\"lazy\">\n  </a>\n    </span> </figure>\n<h4 id=\"molinos-which-grind-the-chocolate-turning-it-into-cocoa-liquor\"><a href=\"#molinos-which-grind-the-chocolate-turning-it-into-cocoa-liquor\" aria-label=\"molinos which grind the chocolate turning it into cocoa liquor permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Molinos which grind the chocolate turning it into cocoa liquor.</h4>\n<figure> <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 751px;\">\n      <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/b385d9da1d56200b48db6d3d29a7d297/81705/81-9.jpg\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 74.96671105193076%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/jpeg;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"81 9\" title=\"81 9\" src=\"/static/b385d9da1d56200b48db6d3d29a7d297/81705/81-9.jpg\" srcset=\"/static/b385d9da1d56200b48db6d3d29a7d297/90185/81-9.jpg 450w,\n/static/b385d9da1d56200b48db6d3d29a7d297/81705/81-9.jpg 751w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 751px) 100vw, 751px\" loading=\"lazy\">\n  </a>\n    </span> </figure>\n<h4 id=\"more-chocolate-samples\"><a href=\"#more-chocolate-samples\" aria-label=\"more chocolate samples permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>More chocolate samples!</h4>\n<figure> <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 653px;\">\n      <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/f2b9eede2efb0dfafdb878a84aff521e/0e887/81-7.jpg\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 75.03828483920367%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/jpeg;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"81 7\" title=\"81 7\" src=\"/static/f2b9eede2efb0dfafdb878a84aff521e/0e887/81-7.jpg\" srcset=\"/static/f2b9eede2efb0dfafdb878a84aff521e/90185/81-7.jpg 450w,\n/static/f2b9eede2efb0dfafdb878a84aff521e/0e887/81-7.jpg 653w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 653px) 100vw, 653px\" loading=\"lazy\">\n  </a>\n    </span> </figure>\n<p>Tours currently run from Tuesday thru Sunday and are only $5 per person.  The slots do fill up quickly and reservations are required.  So if you happen to be in the Somerville area and have a craving for chocolate (they give out a lot of samples) and chocolate knowledge, then Taza is definitely a good place to visit.</p>","timeToRead":4,"excerpt":"I don't know how many of you have heard of Taza Chocolate, but up in Somerville and Cambridge, they've become a pretty big deal among the…","frontmatter":{"title":"Taza Chocolate Factory Tour","image":{"feature":{"publicURL":"/static/81-1-63ec3918b23f8c5cdd8e3a81379ee7c1.jpg","childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/jpeg;base64,","aspectRatio":1.2855029585798816,"src":"/static/63ec3918b23f8c5cdd8e3a81379ee7c1/b17c1/81-1.jpg","srcSet":"/static/63ec3918b23f8c5cdd8e3a81379ee7c1/00e5e/81-1.jpg 200w,\n/static/63ec3918b23f8c5cdd8e3a81379ee7c1/1a903/81-1.jpg 400w,\n/static/63ec3918b23f8c5cdd8e3a81379ee7c1/b17c1/81-1.jpg 800w,\n/static/63ec3918b23f8c5cdd8e3a81379ee7c1/e5e2c/81-1.jpg 869w","sizes":"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px"}}}},"feature_video":null,"date":"2014-06-24","categories":["blog"],"tags":["blog","chocolate","sweets","tour"]},"fields":{"slug":"/blog/taza-chocolate-factory-tour","date":"2014-06-23T23:00:00.000Z"}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/blog/taza-chocolate-factory-tour","nextslug":"/recipes/flakey-chinese-scallion-pancakes","prevslug":"/recipes/coconut-rum-cake"}}}